cell: Flagpole

The flagpole was once located at 10 St. between D and E Sts. at Williams Air Force Base. It is now located at the entrance of the Phoenix-Mesa Gateway Airport which is located on the grounds which once belonged to Williams AFB. , 33°18′25″N 111°40′45″W﻿ / ﻿33.30694°N 111.67917°W
Flagpole erected in 1941 by Del E. Webb Construction Company
